All right. That's all I have. Thanks very much for your time.

633
00:41:35,380 --> 00:41:38,760
下士在車上等著，他會送你們回機場
Corporal's waiting with the Jeep. He'll take you back to the flight line.

634
00:41:38,760 --> 00:41:40,800
