Of course.

693
00:45:02,590 --> 00:45:06,130
去機場時下士會送你們去人事部門…
Corporal will take you by personnel on your way out to the flight line...

694
00:45:06,130 --> 00:45:10,510
你可以複印你想要的所有調令
and you can have all the transfer orders that you want.

695
00:45:11,470 --> 00:45:14,760
走吧 但你們得對我客氣點
Let's go. But you have to ask me nicely.

696
00:45:17,020 --> 00:45:18,310
